filter_description:
Currently, label and creation time filtering is supported, which needs to be filled in according to the following format:

{

"tags": {

"$and": ["tag 1","tag 2"],

"$or": ["When there is $and tag, and takes effect, or does not take effect"]

},

"createTime": {

"$gte": "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm format is sufficient. The creation time of the collection is greater than this time",

"$lte": "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm format is sufficient. The creation time of the collection is less than this time. It can be used together with $gte"

}

}
